lead_paragraph: Henrik Lundqvist made 40 saves in his first game since March 3, but a goal by Darren Helm in overtime gave the Red Wings a 3-2 win over the Rangers.

headline.print_headline: Red Wings Spoil Strong Lundqvist Start
